{"tid":1244050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！香討有人呼籲621出黎","createTime":"2019-06-19T17:17:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T08:54:52.000Z","uid":58307,"like":1199,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":117,"replies":[{"pid":"6f58a69866f52df7738f6a301b1237a35b43eb74","tid":1244050,"uid":58307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T17:17:52.000Z","msg":"係香討見到好多post話621政總見！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4NTZE11.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4NTZE11.png&h=70e04537&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"18175a216d4871c77099f0bc1355cae5b8d66254","tid":1244050,"uid":212182,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T17:18:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0a3902e1a8da9ebbba2e5bc3109ac4007bad559a","tid":1244050,"uid":254729,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T17:18:51.000Z","msg":"621圍立法會定禮賓府<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1243737\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1243737</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b2b9b2866f8cb470ad097e762a712d40b385a69c","tid":1244050,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T17:19:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc8c0966fa55dd2d239e0fb17a7ad5595f9003f8","tid":1244050,"uid":261627,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T17:19:17.000Z","msg":"求各路巴絲推依個穩民心<br />\n推埋上 ig(求屌醒)621要做乜？我乜都唔知 點解要出？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1244018\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1244018</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bf3a335f193a8761f17b227fb3109f4ab98da24b","tid":1244050,"uid":129243,"like":145,"dislike":1,"score":144,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T17:19:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd772d0141ab21e78dea7351cbca17540e1390c3","tid":1244050,"uid":710,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T17:20:13.000Z"